WEBVTT

00:02.001 --> 00:03.334
<i> ["The Ballad</i>
    <i> Of Gilligan's Island"]</i>

00:03.403 --> 00:05.771
¶ Just sit right back
    and you'll hear a tale ¶

00:05.840 --> 00:07.739
¶ A tale of a fateful trip ¶

00:07.808 --> 00:12.277
¶ That started from this tropic
port aboard this tiny ship ¶

00:12.346 --> 00:14.813
¶ The mate was
     a mighty sailing man ¶

00:14.882 --> 00:17.115
¶ The skipper brave and sure ¶

00:17.184 --> 00:19.518
¶ Five passengers
      set sail that day ¶

00:19.586 --> 00:21.720
¶ For a three hour tour ¶

00:21.789 --> 00:24.689
¶ A three hour tour ¶

00:24.758 --> 00:26.691
[thunder rumbling]

00:26.760 --> 00:28.860
¶ The weather started
     getting rough ¶

00:28.929 --> 00:31.196
¶ The tiny ship was tossed ¶

00:31.264 --> 00:33.799
¶ If not for the courage
    of the fearless crew ¶

00:33.868 --> 00:35.901
¶ The Minnow would be lost ¶

00:35.970 --> 00:38.303
¶ The Minnow would be lost ¶

00:38.372 --> 00:40.606
¶ The ship set ground
     on the shore ¶

00:40.674 --> 00:43.074
¶ Of this
    uncharted desert isle ¶

00:43.143 --> 00:45.309
¶ With Gilligan ¶

00:45.378 --> 00:47.779
¶ The Skipper too ¶

00:47.848 --> 00:49.781
¶ The millionaire ¶

00:49.850 --> 00:52.150
¶ And his wife ¶

00:52.219 --> 00:55.220
¶ The movie star ¶

00:55.289 --> 01:01.360
¶ And the rest are here
    on Gilligan's Isle ¶

